channel.title: [delta] Commands randomly stopped working
channel.description:
Well i dont even think i edited anything in commands part of client.java but somereason commands stopped working. ::pickup isnt working for admin or owner (which its set to admin+). ::master aint working for admin or owner like its set to. ::pure isnt working for players or my owner account (i set ::pure rights to 0 lastnight n i tested it and it was working)
All my commands was working perfectly lastnight and i dont think i change anything that should effect them.. and now non of them are working at all.. compiler is not picking up any errors.. anybody know whats wrong and how to fix?
